187
00:16:06.553 --> 00:16:08.179
You asking or telling?

188
00:16:08.217 --> 00:16:10.673
That is what we want.

189
00:16:10.714 --> 00:16:12.983
I thought the cattles,
you drive them north, too.


190
00:16:13.017 --> 00:16:14.676
With many peoples.

