00:16:14.714 --> 00:16:16.208
With iron trains.

192
00:16:16.249 --> 00:16:17.249
That is what we want.

193
00:16:17.274 --> 00:16:18.751
These beeves
don't speak ingles.


194
00:16:18.990 --> 00:16:21.990
They speak...
espanol.


195
00:16:22.842 --> 00:16:24.882
What do you want for her?

196
00:16:24.922 --> 00:16:26.962
The tigre is not for sale,
senor.


197
00:16:27.002 --> 00:16:28.017
What about her?

198
00:16:28.985 --> 00:16:31.669
She is my wife, senor.

199
00:16:31.705 --> 00:16:32.753
What's she do?

200
00:16:34.393 --> 00:16:35.637
What's she do?!

201
00:16:35.674 --> 00:16:37.332
She acrobat, senor.

202
00:16:37.369 --> 00:16:39.204
She spins and balances
and juggles.


203
00:16:39.237 --> 00:16:41.261
Well, if she can juggle
three balls in the air


204
00:16:41.498 --> 00:16:43.953
without dropping one of them,
you can keep your tomcat.


205
